Name: CAP STATION BEARING CODE
Explanation: A 2-NUMERIC CODE WHICH INDICATES THE TRUE BEARING, IN TENS OF DEGREES, OF A COMBAT AIR PATROL (CAP) STATION FROM A REFERENCE POINT, USUALLY THE CENTRE OF THE FORCE.

Name: BEARING FROM REFERENCE POINT IN DEGREES, TRUE
LEFT AREA BOUNDARY IN DEGREES TRUE
RIGHT AREA BOUNDARY IN DEGREES TRUE
